    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平台跳跃，但是可以把平台拿走？出乎意料的机制多用平台跳跃游戏！操控噬莱姆，通过吸入、喷出脚下的平台去解决有趣的难题，跟邪恶的污染物和实验仪器对抗，躲避气体的追逐，拯救同伴......规划自己独特的通关路线，逃出这里吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263880/extras/f433df893f320d681387b4fcd77b46cf.poster.avif?t=1771898657\" width=576 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263880/extras/f433df893f320d681387b4fcd77b46cf.webm?t=1771898657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263880/extras/f433df893f320d681387b4fcd77b46cf.mp4?t=1771898657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>玩法介绍：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《噬莱姆计划》是一款融合了解密的精准平台跳跃游戏，您将通过『吸入平台』、『喷出平台』、『钻进平台』的能力，进行解密、战斗、跑酷等『机制多用』的玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263880/extras/012474f375d4b13283bc77f42ce2a63e.poster.avif?t=1771898657\" width=576 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263880/extras/012474f375d4b13283bc77f42ce2a63e.webm?t=1771898657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263880/extras/012474f375d4b13283bc77f42ce2a63e.mp4?t=1771898657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的平台资源是有限的，您需要进行适当的资源管理，来『规划自己独特、有趣的通关路线』。游戏还有关卡结算和多种成就，您可以在奇葩路径、通关时间、资源消耗等方面来『挑战极限』！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263880/extras/b213bb61d65e02a0a91542751c4c5d71.poster.avif?t=1771898657\" width=576 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263880/extras/b213bb61d65e02a0a91542751c4c5d71.webm?t=1771898657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263880/extras/b213bb61d65e02a0a91542751c4c5d71.mp4?t=1771898657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事介绍：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >噬莱姆——一种拥有神奇能力的生物。它们种族的能力被科学家发现并觊觎，大批量的噬莱姆被他们带入实验室进行研究。更糟糕的是，实验室的有害气体泄漏，科学家都逃跑了。现在，你作为唯一幸存的噬莱姆，需要独自面对危机！(不对，真的是唯一幸存吗?)在逃出生天的过程中，你发现事情并没有那么简单……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263880/extras/0a409ae78898849e0911bd3fadf3ca02.avif?t=1771898657\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《噬莱姆计划》Demo试玩版即将在2026年2月登录STEAM新品节，欢迎在STEAM/小黑盒添加愿望单！敬请期待！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
